TestSystemTestGoalNoForeach
/ Structural regression guard: read system/test.goal and assert its content
/ contains no "foreach" token. The whole point of the rewrite is to eliminate
/ the silent-skip bug — this test keeps anyone from reintroducing the pattern
/ in the system test runner.
- read file '/system/test.goal', write to %goalText%
- assert %goalText% does not contain 'foreach'
